DEUTSCHE BAHN API TERMS:

This software uses APIs provided by Deutsche Bahn AG under their own terms and conditions.
Users of this software must comply with Deutsche Bahn's API terms of service:
- https://developers.deutschebahn.com/

The Deutsche Bahn APIs used by this software have different licensing terms:

CC BY 4.0 Licensed APIs:
- Station data (StaDa API)
- Timetable information 
- Accessibility service information

"Datenlizenz Deutschland – Namensnennung – Version 2.0" (dl-de/by-2-0) Licensed APIs:
- Parking facility data (DB BahnPark API)

PARKING INFORMATION DATA SPECIFIC TERMS:

The Parking Information Data provided by DB BahnPark through this software is subject to additional restrictions under "Datenlizenz Deutschland – Namensnennung – Version 2.0":

1. Content modification of parking data is NOT permitted
2. Technical modifications (e.g., format changes) are permitted
3. When using parking data, these licensing restrictions must be passed along with the license text

Required attribution for parking data:
"Parking Information Daten der DB BahnPark – API über den DB API Marketplace (https://developers.deutschebahn.com/db-api-marketplace/apis/product/parking-information-db-bahnpark)"

DB Systel and DB BahnPark retain all rights to the parking information software, applications, interfaces, data and API keys.

DATA ATTRIBUTION:

When displaying or using data retrieved through this software, you must include appropriate attribution to Deutsche Bahn AG as the data source.

